## kramdown2 2.4.0 released

A minor release bringing a small enhancement to the kramdown2 converter and some bug fixes.

## Changes

* 1 minor change:

  - Allow using a different list indentation (pull request [#753] by Carsten Borman)

* 2 bug fixes:

  - Fixed escaping of colon when converting to kramdown2 (fixes [#751] by Carsten Borman)
  - Fixed setting highlighter class for code spans in HTML converter when using a default language
    (fixes [#752] by Aswhin Maroli)

